# 📘 n8n – Workflow Automation Tool Notes

## 🧠 What is n8n?

**n8n** (pronounced "n-eight-n") is an **open-source workflow automation tool** that connects apps, APIs, and services to automate tasks and data flows. It offers powerful integration and customization options using a visual interface.

---

## 🚀 Key Features

- 🔓 **Open Source** – Fair-code licensed and can be self-hosted.
- 🧩 **350+ Built-in Nodes** – For apps like Google Sheets, Slack, Trello, etc.
- 🖱️ **Visual Workflow Builder** – Drag-and-drop UI for designing automations.
- 🧠 **Custom JavaScript Support** – For logic and data transformation.
- ⏰ **Flexible Triggers** – Webhooks, cron jobs, polling, etc.
- 🔀 **Conditional Logic** – Use `IF`, `Switch`, and error handling nodes.
- ☁️ **Scalable Deployment** – Self-host or use [n8n.cloud](https://n8n.io/).

---

## 🛠️ Core Components

| Component     | Description                                         |
|--------------|-----------------------------------------------------|
| **Node**      | A step in the workflow (e.g., HTTP request, Slack). |
| **Workflow**  | A chain of nodes defining the automation.           |
| **Trigger**   | Starts the workflow (e.g., webhook, schedule).      |
| **Execution** | A run instance of a workflow.                       |

---

## 📦 Installation Options

- **Self-hosted**
  - Docker (recommended)
  - `npm install n8n` (for local development)
- **Cloud**
  - Official service: [n8n.cloud](https://n8n.cloud)

---

## 💼 Common Use Cases

- Automating CRM or lead tracking
- Syncing data between apps (e.g., Airtable ↔ Google Sheets)
- Webhook-based API workflows
- Sending notifications (Slack, Discord, Email)
- Daily/weekly report generation
- Scraping, monitoring, and alerting tasks

---

## 🧩 Example Node Types

| Type         | Examples                         |
|--------------|----------------------------------|
| **Triggers** | Webhook, Cron, IMAP Email        |
| **Apps**     | Google Sheets, Airtable, Notion  |
| **Dev Tools**| HTTP Request, Function, Set      |
| **Messaging**| Slack, Discord, Telegram         |
| **Database** | MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB       |
| **Logic**    | IF, Switch, Merge                |

---

## 🔐 Authentication & Security

- Supports **OAuth2**, **API Key**, **Basic Auth**
- Credentials securely stored
- Role-based access (cloud/enterprise features)

