---

## ⚖️ Pros & Cons

| ✅ Pros                          | ❌ Cons                          |
|----------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Open-source & self-hostable      | Steeper learning curve           |
| Highly customizable workflows    | Requires some technical setup    |
| JavaScript support for logic     | UI can be overwhelming at first  |
| Active community & docs          | Self-hosting needs maintenance   |

