## 🧪 Example Use Case (Optional Section)

> **Use Case**: Send a Slack message every time a new row is added to Google Sheets.
>
> **Workflow**:
> 1. **Trigger**: Google Sheets (New Row)
> 2. **Node**: Slack (Send Message)
> 3. **Optional**: Add logic with `IF` or `Function` node

